  <brief_title>Tricuspid Isthmus Imaged by CARTOsound, Patients With Typical Atrial Flutter</brief_title>
  <official_title>Tricuspid Isthmus Architecture as Imaged by CARTOsound, Determines Ablation Times in Patients With Typical Atrial Flutter</official_title>
